00:28:31,930 --> 00:28:33,640
I'll rehearse more effectively with her.

593
00:28:34,390 --> 00:28:35,640
She's acting on your behalf.

594
00:28:36,100 --> 00:28:37,300
You don't want her to mess up.

595
00:28:39,640 --> 00:28:40,800
But

596
00:28:40,890 --> 00:28:42,970
how should I tell Chen Jing'an?

597
00:28:44,970 --> 00:28:45,850
No need.

598
00:28:46,600 --> 00:28:47,540
I'll go straight to her.

599
00:28:49,050 --> 00:28:49,890
Good.

600
00:28:51,390 --> 00:28:52,230
Thanks.

601
00:29:04,140 --> 00:29:05,140
I was just thinking

602
00:29:05,720 --> 00:29:07,720
Jing'an's lucky
to have a brother like you.

603
00:29:19,260 --> 00:29:20,510
(Romeo and Juliet Script)

604
00:29:27,390 --> 00:29:28,350
You did all this?

605
00:29:31,300 --> 00:29:33,430
I even recorded some lines.

606
00:29:33,890 --> 00:29:35,680
If you're unsure about the emotions,

607
00:29:35,890 --> 00:29:36,930
you can refer to this.

608
00:29:38,890 --> 00:29:40,300
Isn't this my Walkman?

609
00:29:42,800 --> 00:29:43,640
What,

610
00:29:43,640 --> 00:29:45,430
afraid I'll embarrass you again?

611
00:29:46,680 --> 00:29:47,550
Yes.

612
00:29:48,430 --> 00:29:50,890
You already humiliated me
in the last speech contest.

613
00:29:51,180 --> 00:29:53,220
This time, don't ruin the play.

614
00:29:53,220 --> 00:29:54,100
Got it?

615
00:29:54,300 --> 00:29:55,390
You really don't trust me?

616
00:29:55,390 --> 00:29:56,970
You think I can't do anything right?

617
00:29:57,550 --> 00:29:58,390
Jing'an,

618
00:29:58,550 --> 00:30:00,430
don't stress too much.

619
00:30:00,600 --> 00:30:02,800
This isn't your strength anyway.

620
00:30:02,930 --> 00:30:04,390
Just do your best.

621
00:30:05,100 --> 00:30:05,940
Besides,

622
00:30:06,140 --> 00:30:08,300
this was originally my task.

623
00:30:08,600 --> 00:30:09,640
I'm just grateful

624
00:30:09,640 --> 00:30:11,220
you're helping me.

625
00:30:12,930 --> 00:30:13,890
You're welcome.

626
00:30:16,640 --> 00:30:17,480
Actually,

627
00:30:17,850 --> 00:30:19,390
I've thought about

628
00:30:19,390 --> 00:30:20,850
what you said.

629
00:30:21,930 --> 00:30:23,050
A lot of times,

630
00:30:23,140 --> 00:30:25,140
I struggle to say no

631
00:30:25,850 --> 00:30:28,890
or express my true feelings.

632
00:30:29,600 --> 00:30:31,220
I'll work on changing that.

633
00:30:34,550 --> 00:30:35,390
Honestly,

634
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:36,680
I was wrong too.

635
00:30:37,050 --> 00:30:38,140
Back then,

636
00:30:38,140 --> 00:30:39,240
I only thought about myself

637
00:30:39,240 --> 00:30:40,640
and ignored your feelings.

638
00:30:40,890 --> 00:30:41,760
I'm sorry.

639
00:30:42,640 --> 00:30:43,640
It's fine.

640
00:30:44,890 --> 00:30:45,730
So…

641
00:30:45,930 --> 00:30:47,220
are we good now?

642
00:30:48,800 --> 00:30:50,930
I wasn't that mad anyway.

643
00:30:52,050 --> 00:30:53,600
I just said those things in anger.

644
00:30:53,600 --> 00:30:54,720
I regretted it right after.

645
00:30:55,140 --> 00:30:57,220
Let's rehearse after school.

646
00:30:57,640 --> 00:30:58,720
Next practice,

647
00:30:58,890 --> 00:31:00,300
we'll surprise everyone.

648
00:31:00,430 --> 00:31:01,300
Deal.

649
00:31:06,010 --> 00:31:08,600
(Grade 11)

650
00:31:10,800 --> 00:31:12,640
Chen Jing'an, how's your draft?

651
00:31:13,390 --> 00:31:14,390
Only halfway done.

652
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:17,350
Niannian's an experienced host.

653
00:31:17,350 --> 00:31:18,640
Let's ask her after school

654
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:19,720
to review your draft

655
00:31:19,720 --> 00:31:21,050
and give you some tips.

656
00:31:21,390 --> 00:31:22,600
She's right.

657
00:31:23,140 --> 00:31:25,050
You should ask Zhu Niannian for help.

658
00:31:25,350 --> 00:31:27,640
That way,
competing with you will be fun.

659
00:31:28,430 --> 00:31:29,390
No need.

660
00:31:29,580 --> 00:31:31,100
I'll write it myself.

661
00:31:32,720 --> 00:31:34,140
You're an amateur.

662
00:31:34,140 --> 00:31:35,800
Why so stubborn?

663
00:31:36,970 --> 00:31:37,850
Chen Jing'an,

664
00:31:38,180 --> 00:31:39,340
with Niannian's guidance,

665
00:31:39,340 --> 00:31:40,970
you might even place well.

666
00:31:42,700 --> 00:31:43,550
Alright,

667
00:31:43,550 --> 00:31:45,350
I'll go see her later.

668
00:31:46,430 --> 00:31:47,890
Then tell her this:

669
00:31:47,890 --> 00:31:48,730
Whether it's her

670
00:31:48,730 --> 00:31:49,850
or her apprentice,

671
00:31:50,100 --> 00:31:51,180
I'll win.

672
00:31:55,390 --> 00:31:56,300
Ignore her.

673
00:31:56,300 --> 00:31:57,550
Just focus on your draft.

674
00:31:57,680 --> 00:31:59,220
When this class ends,

675
00:31:59,220 --> 00:32:00,220
I'll find Niannian

676
00:32:00,220 --> 00:32:02,100
and ask her to help you

677
00:32:02,390 --> 00:32:03,350
after school.

678
00:32:04,430 --> 00:32:07,640
We have a play rehearsal after school.

679
00:32:09,180 --> 00:32:10,470
Just the two of you?

680
00:32:11,100 --> 00:32:11,940
Yeah.

681
00:32:36,720 --> 00:32:38,300
Can I join?

682
00:32:38,930 --> 00:32:40,350
Probably not.

683
00:32:40,350 --> 00:32:42,220
Niannian only invited me.

684
00:32:45,890 --> 00:32:48,390
Guess you're completely out of favor.

685
00:32:59,550 --> 00:33:01,350
Do you love me?

686
00:33:01,850 --> 00:33:03,640
I know you'll say yes.

687
00:33:04,390 --> 00:33:06,600
My dear, gentle Romeo,

688
00:33:06,680 --> 00:33:07,800
if you truly love me,

689
00:33:08,100 --> 00:33:09,640
show me with sincerity.

690
00:33:15,720 --> 00:33:16,680
Why are you here?

691
00:33:18,180 --> 00:33:19,050
I came to rehearse.

692
00:33:20,850 --> 00:33:21,690
Rehearse what?

693
00:33:23,050 --> 00:33:24,100
Romeo and Juliet.

694
00:33:25,010 --> 00:33:26,220
(Romeo and Juliet Script)

695
00:33:29,720 --> 00:33:31,430
Chen Jing'an asked me
to help you rehearse.

696
00:33:33,890 --> 00:33:35,300
She didn't tell me.

697
00:33:36,800 --> 00:33:37,640
Maybe she forgot.

698
00:33:38,640 --> 00:33:39,600
When she comes,

699
00:33:40,390 --> 00:33:41,490
have her tell you herself.

700
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:44,510
Whatever.

701
00:33:45,300 --> 00:33:47,220
Better than rehearsing alone.

702
00:33:48,100 --> 00:33:49,390
You play the guy.

703
00:33:49,510 --> 00:33:50,550
Let's do the rehearsal.

704
00:33:50,760 --> 00:33:51,600
Okay.

705
00:34:00,760 --> 00:34:02,640
Don't deny you love him in front of me.

706
00:34:03,100 --> 00:34:05,050
I'll admit I love him to your face.

707
00:34:06,890 --> 00:34:07,890
Your tone's wrong.

708
00:34:08,640 --> 00:34:10,180
That's not how Juliet speaks.

709
00:34:10,850 --> 00:34:11,690
Too harsh.

710
00:34:12,640 --> 00:34:14,430
But she's being forced into marriage.

711
00:34:14,640 --> 00:34:15,890
She loves Romeo so much,

712
00:34:17,050 --> 00:34:19,220
and Paris is so annoying.

713
00:34:21,180 --> 00:34:22,350
Shouldn't she be angry?

714
00:34:23,640 --> 00:34:24,890
Juliet's a noble lady.

715
00:34:25,640 --> 00:34:26,930
Even if she resists the marriage,

716
00:34:27,390 --> 00:34:28,850
she wouldn't be rude.

717
00:34:29,640 --> 00:34:31,100
Then what's the point?

718
00:34:31,100 --> 00:34:32,390
Having to be polite

719
00:34:32,640 --> 00:34:33,640
to someone you hate.

720
00:34:33,640 --> 00:34:35,100
The audience would be frustrated.

721
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:36,800
So to you,

722
00:34:38,430 --> 00:34:39,800
being rude means

723
00:34:40,890 --> 00:34:41,930
you dislike someone?

724
00:34:41,990 --> 00:34:42,850
Obviously.

725
00:34:42,850 --> 00:34:43,600
Or should I say,

726
00:34:43,600 --> 00:34:44,640
"I like you" to them?

727
00:34:47,640 --> 00:34:48,640
Why talk about this?

728
00:34:48,640 --> 00:34:49,800
Let's focus on the script.

729
00:34:55,100 --> 00:34:56,350
Jing'an, you're finally here.

730
00:34:56,470 --> 00:34:57,640
Why'd you bring your brother?

731
00:34:57,640 --> 00:34:59,470
He's bossy and unhelpful.

732
00:35:00,550 --> 00:35:01,640
Sorry.

733
00:35:01,890 --> 00:35:03,890
But Tian Ye's group is rehearsing too.

734
00:35:03,970 --> 00:35:05,390
I had no choice.

735
00:35:10,220 --> 00:35:11,640
I'm not blaming you.

736
00:35:11,890 --> 00:35:12,730
But...

737
00:35:12,970 --> 00:35:14,140
a Romeo like him

738
00:35:14,140 --> 00:35:15,350
saying he'll elope with me?

739
00:35:16,140 --> 00:35:17,720
Not romantic at all.

740
00:35:18,140 --> 00:35:19,600
I'd just call the police.

741
00:35:19,720 --> 00:35:21,050
"Help, police!"

742
00:35:23,050 --> 00:35:24,550
- Am I that scary?
- Very scary.

743
00:35:25,350 --> 00:35:27,140
For the play's sake,

744
00:35:27,220 --> 00:35:28,550
just bear with him, okay?

745
00:35:33,970 --> 00:35:34,850
Fine.

746
00:35:35,100 --> 00:35:36,390
I'll do it for you,

747
00:35:36,930 --> 00:35:38,140
rehearsing with him.

748
00:35:38,720 --> 00:35:39,720
We're short on time.

749
00:35:39,720 --> 00:35:41,180
Let's start rehearsing.

750
00:35:41,640 --> 00:35:43,220
First, the farewell scene.

751
00:35:43,220 --> 00:35:44,640
It's crucial.

752
00:35:44,850 --> 00:35:46,130
- Okay.
- Alright.

753
00:35:50,430 --> 00:35:52,100
Then let day in,

754
00:35:52,100 --> 00:35:53,390
and let life out.

755
00:35:54,220 --> 00:35:55,100
Farewell,

756
00:35:55,430 --> 00:35:56,300
farewell!

757
00:35:57,300 --> 00:35:58,220
One kiss,

758
00:35:58,800 --> 00:35:59,720
and I'll descend.

759
00:36:00,550 --> 00:36:02,140
Are you leaving so? My lord.

760
00:36:03,970 --> 00:36:04,890
Wait a moment.

761
00:36:06,600 --> 00:36:07,440
What's wrong?

762
00:36:08,050 --> 00:36:08,890
I just think...

763
00:36:08,890 --> 00:36:10,890
your line delivery

764
00:36:10,890 --> 00:36:12,390
sounds too stiff.

765
00:36:13,390 --> 00:36:14,390
You're playing

766
00:36:14,640 --> 00:36:16,550
lovers now.

767
00:36:16,640 --> 00:36:18,890
Even friends hug when parting.

768
00:36:19,430 --> 00:36:21,140
Otherwise, it looks fake.

769
00:36:21,300 --> 00:36:23,350
The audience will criticize you.

770
00:36:26,140 --> 00:36:27,600
But we can't hug.

771
00:36:28,850 --> 00:36:29,690
That'd be so awkward.

772
00:36:30,850 --> 00:36:31,720
Maybe hand-holding.

773
00:36:33,220 --> 00:36:34,970
Let's try it like this first.

774
00:36:42,680 --> 00:36:43,550
Don't move.

775
00:36:44,140 --> 00:36:45,010
Now say your lines.

776
00:36:50,430 --> 00:36:51,300
Then...

777
00:36:51,600 --> 00:36:52,440
farewell,

778
00:36:53,930 --> 00:36:54,800
my...

779
00:36:55,220 --> 00:36:56,100
friend,

780
00:36:57,850 --> 00:36:58,690
my lord,

781
00:36:58,890 --> 00:36:59,890
my love.

782
00:37:03,180 --> 00:37:04,050
We'll meet again,

783
00:37:04,640 --> 00:37:05,480
my beloved.

784
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:07,470
I'll never miss a chance

785
00:37:08,640 --> 00:37:09,890
to show you my heart.

786
00:37:31,806 --> 00:37:34,766
♪Sweetness flows like honey♪

787
00:37:35,126 --> 00:37:38,286
♪Warm hugs rest on my chest♪

788
00:37:39,016 --> 00:37:42,866
♪Running together toward wild happiness♪

789
00:37:42,886 --> 00:37:45,406
♪Shining just like this♪

790
00:37:45,406 --> 00:37:48,446
♪Every day is glowing♪

791
00:37:48,876 --> 00:37:52,216
♪Your love makes me strong♪

792
00:37:52,676 --> 00:37:55,566
♪With you in my future,
I'm not lost anymore♪

